text: Rifal Lastori (born June 9, 1997), is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a winger for Liga 2 club Sulut United, on loan from Borneo. == Honours == === Club === PSIS Semarang * Liga 2 Third place (play-offs): 2017 PSS Sleman * Liga 2: 2018 ==References== == External links == * Rifal Lastori at Liga Indonesia * Rifal Lastori at Soccerway Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Borneo F.C. players Category:PSIS Semarang players Category:PSS Sleman players Category:Liga 2 (Indonesia) players Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players Category:Indonesia youth international footballers Category:Association football wingers
